---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="Logical Fallacies">
  <article class="font-lxgw">
    <h1 class="text-text10 text-2xl font-semibold">什么是逻辑谬误？</h1>
    <p class="mt-4">
      逻辑谬误是心智模型中出现的逻辑错误，这些逻辑错误往往不容易被发觉。逻辑谬误可以分为


      <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Formal_fallacy">形式逻辑谬误</a> 和


      <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Informal_fallacy">非形式逻辑谬误</a
      >

       。 以下是一些常见的逻辑谬误。
    </p>

    <section class="grid grid-cols-2">
      <div class="bg-blue10 pt-5 pl-6 rounded-lg relative">
        <div
          class="bg-blue10 rounded-full absolute p-3 flex items-center justify-center top-0 left-0">
          <img src="/flames/orange.svg" alt="flames" width="32" height="32" />
        </div>
        <article class="bg-blue20 rounded-lg py-8 px-11 shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-text10">稻草人谬误</h2>
          <p class="text-base mt-3 text-text10">
            During my review, I take notes detailing actionable steps you can
            take to improve, as well as any valuable thoughts I have during my
            time with your project.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
